OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778151777
OL,3,CPeregrine falcon chicks hatch at the
OL,4,CUniversity of Leeds
OL,6,FFour peregrine falcon chicks have
OL,7,Fhatched in the nest at the University
OL,8,Fof Leeds.
OL,10,FThe four eggs were laid in March with
OL,11,Fpeople tuning in regularly to the
OL,12,FUniversity's live stream of the nest
OL,13,Fin order to catch a glimpse of them
OL,14,Fhatching.
OL,16,FThe first egg hatched on Wednesday
OL,17,Fafternoon, with the other chicks
OL,18,Fmaking their hatching in the following
OL,19,Fhours.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
