CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778151777
OL,3,CPeregrine falcon chicks hatch at the
OL,4,CUniversity of Leeds
OL,6,FA university spokesperson said: "So
OL,7,Fmany people logged on to the
OL,8,FUniversity website to get a glimpse of
OL,9,Fthe new arrivals that the livestream
OL,10,Fcrashed several times."
OL,12,FMichael Howroyd, of the University's
OL,13,FSustainability Projects Officer and
OL,14,FBiodiversity Programme, said: "To have
OL,15,Fall four peregrine eggs successfully
OL,16,Fhatching on the Parkinson tower is
OL,17,Fwonderful and the whole community at
OL,18,FLeeds is thrilled with our new
OL,19,Farrivals.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
