OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778151777
OL,3,CPeregrine falcon chicks hatch at the
OL,4,CUniversity of Leeds
OL,6,F"We are really looking forward to
OL,7,Fseeing them grow over the next few
OL,8,Fweeks, and hope to provide a home for
OL,9,Fmany more generations of peregrines
OL,10,Ffor years to come.
OL,12,F"It's great to see that, thanks to our
OL,13,Ffocus on biodiversity, many species of
OL,14,Fwildlife choose to call our campus
OL,15,Fhome."
OL,17,FPeregrines first nested at the
OL,18,Funiversity in 2018 and have been
OL,19,Fcoming back intermittently ever since.
OL,20,FSo far 14 chicks have hatched
OL,21,Fsuccessfully atop the tower.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@FO]
