OL,3,CPeregrine falcon chicks hatch at the
OL,4,CUniversity of Leeds
OL,6,FThis years female falcon is known as
OL,7,F'7.H' and can be identified by the
OL,8,Fring on her leg. The university say
OL,9,Fshe hatched in in Stoke-on-Trent six
OL,10,Fyears ago, whilst the male has not
OL,11,Fbeen ringed.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
